    "created_at": "2016-07-27T16:11:01Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-07-27T16:11:01Z",
    "body": "Yep! I'm aware - the full command we use in that commit above is `xdg-mime default nylas.desktop x-scheme-handler/#{scheme}`. I only bring it up because it has been successfully making N1 the default handler for the mailto protocol on Debian systems and might be more broadly incorporated into Electron. \n"
